{"tid":1286842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[表揚]大家都開始識得唔覆分化撚","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T03:45:27.000Z","uid":237517,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3e312f43db47a321bd54925f624a62d6035145","tid":1286842,"uid":237517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"有段時間會見到一堆近似內容既PO一齊出現(例如唔好XXX, 快D走, 咩咩係鬼, 誰誰背景有問題, FAKE NEWS 等)<br />\n<br />\n開始會每個PO都回, 想澄清<br />\n<br />\n後來發現愈回愈係置頂<br />\n<br />\n因為人係見標題大過睇內容既動物<br />\n<br />\n回覆變左幫佢宣揚分化訊息<br />\n<br />\n後面就變成只要講過我想講既野就唔回<br />\n<br />\n唔衝動唔幫佢推PO<br />\n<br />\n而家發現, 唔知幾時開始, 大家都好似做緊差不多既野<br />\n<br />\n見我突登唔回既PO會慢慢洗走, 停留時間短左好多<br />\n<br />\n原來大家都在默默進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e82037af028e47a19b7f448c6dd5237d2885445","tid":1286842,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:42:40.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3aa501ccc84448e76dcabf775bc80b843ce494e","tid":1286842,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:45:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}